oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Burnout or Boredom?
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Sonsthagen, Teresa F.
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Even the greatest job loses its attraction after awhile and you may start thinking about or even searching for a new job. Do you feel burned out, overworked and underpaid? It must be time to leave! Experts recommend that you think long and hard before quitting. In this presentation, we will discuss five areas to explore before moving to "greener" pastures.
